{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ce90d41ca3","title":"出版说明","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"68068934ba","index":0,"year":1964,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"ce90d41ca3"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"fc1f4280-a408-4802-b905-69179daca249","name":"雇佣劳动与资本（人民出版社1965年版）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"马克思，人民出版社1965年版","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives4/main/fc1f4280-a408-4802-b905-69179daca249.pdf"}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"fc1f4280-a408-4802-b905-69179daca249":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c8b4c38c58","type":"paragraph","text":"出版者明","index":0,"publicationId":"fc1f4280-a408-4802-b905-69179daca249","articleId":"ce90d41ca3"},{"id":"b5ed1f3d20","type":"paragraph","text":"本书正文“座佣劳动与逢本”，是1849年“新莱茵报”所戴原文的文；弗·恩格斯作的“导言”，则是恩格斯在1891年将此书重新校订出版单行本时写的。在这篇导言中，恩格斯明了他对1891年版本所作的某些更改和补充。因此，我们将它排在书前。","index":1,"publicationId":"fc1f4280-a408-4802-b905-69179daca249","articleId":"ce90d41ca3"},{"id":"b6d5c9bdc0","type":"paragraph","text":"马克思的手稿“工瓷”，与“展佣劳动与瓷本”有直接联系，也是对后者的补充，我们把它作为附录收人","index":2,"publicationId":"fc1f4280-a408-4802-b905-69179daca249","articleId":"ce90d41ca3"},{"id":"599e6c8cec","type":"paragraph","text":"本书的正文和附录是根据“马克思恩格斯全集”第六卷人民出版社1961年版文排印的；弗·恩格斯作的“导言”是在“马克思恩格斯文选”两卷集第一卷所戴文的基础上，由中共中央马克思恩格斯列宁斯大林著作局重新校订过的。","index":3,"publicationId":"fc1f4280-a408-4802-b905-69179daca249","articleId":"ce90d41ca3"},{"id":"0a7634deb2","type":"paragraph","text":"1964年3月","index":4,"publicationId":"fc1f4280-a408-4802-b905-69179daca249","articleId":"ce90d41ca3"}],"page":{"id":"5a7364024b","publicationId":"fc1f4280-a408-4802-b905-69179daca249","articleId":"ce90d41ca3","start":4,"end":4}}}},"__N_SSG":true}